# Micro-Savings — Cursor / agent context

<identity>
Micro-Savings is a Vite + vanilla JS frontend with an optional Express + SQLite backend (`backend/`). On-chain flows use **Starkzap** (`StarkZap`, `WalletInterface`), **starknet**, and **@cartridge/controller** on **Sepolia** (see `src/config/starknet.js`).
</identity>

<starkzap_skill>
When changing Starkzap usage, onboarding, paymasters, `Amount`/`Address`, swaps, or lending:

- Read **`starkzap-skill/SKILL.md`** first (gotchas, `ensureReady`, `preflight`, `feeMode`, Cartridge web-only notes).
- Deep dives: **`starkzap-skill/references/`** — `sponsored-transactions.md`, `erc20-helpers.md`, `signer-integration.md`, `staking-reliability.md`.
- The skill text sometimes says **`StarkSDK`**; in this app the npm API is **`StarkZap`** from `starkzap` (same family of patterns).
- Published **`starkzap` v2** includes swap/lending helpers (`wallet.swap`, `wallet.lending()`); the skill’s “no DEX/lending” line reflects an older scope — prefer the installed package’s types and this repo’s `src/flows/sepolia-save-swap-deposit.js` for AVNU/Vesu.
</starkzap_skill>

<structure>
| Path | Purpose |
| --- | --- |
| `src/sdk/starkzap-client.js` | Shared `getStarkZap()` (RPC, chain, explorer) |
| `src/wallet/starkzap-connection.js`, `cartridge-connect.js` | Session + Cartridge connect |
| `src/flows/sepolia-save-swap-deposit.js` | STRK→USDC swap + Vesu deposit pipeline |
| `src/flows/sepolia-pipeline.js` | `runConnectedSaveSwapDeposit` wrapper |
| `backend/` | REST API, cron stub for due saves (`backend/src/jobs/runDueSaves.js`) |
| `docs/USER_WORKFLOW.md` | Product + technical workflow |
</structure>

<conventions>
- ESM only (`"type": "module"`). Match existing JSDoc `@param` style for Starkzap types.
- **`Address`**: use `fromAddress("0x…")` when APIs expect branded `Address` and you only have a string (see skill §1).
- **`Amount`**: `wallet.balanceOf` returns `Amount` — use `.toUnit()`, `.toFormatted()`, `.toBase()` for display/math, not raw concatenation (skill §8).
- **`feeMode: "sponsored"`**: paymaster policy must allow the calls; consider `wallet.preflight` before critical automation (see `starkzap-skill/references/sponsored-transactions.md`).
- Backend cron cannot hold Cartridge sessions; real signing stays **client-side** unless you add a server signer (see `signer-integration.md`).
</conventions>

<commands>
| Task | Command |
| --- | --- |
| Frontend dev | `npm run dev` (root) |
| Backend dev | `cd backend && npm run dev` |
| Frontend build | `npm run build` |
</commands>

<boundaries>
- Do not commit secrets; do not edit `.env` with real keys in-repo.
- Dependency changes to `package.json` / lockfiles: get human approval when policy requires it.
</boundaries>
